<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>체스방 목록 | 체스 시뮬레이터</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/games.css"/>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.png">
</head>
<body>
<section class="header__container">
    {{#gameCount}}
    <h1>체스 시뮬레이터</h1>
    <p>체스 말의 기초적인 움직임을 테스트하기 위한 사이트</p>
    <div>총 {{totalCount}}개의 게임이 생성되었습니다.</div>
    <div>현재 {{runningCount}}개의 게임이 진행 중입니다.</div>
    {{/gameCount}}
</section>
<form id="search-form">
    <label for="num_input">게임 ID</label>
    <input type="number" min="1" id="num_input" name="game_id" placeholder="ex) 1"/>
    <input type="submit" value="검색"/>
</form>
<section class="list__container">
    <div class="title">목록</div>
    <ul>
        {{#games}}
        <li class="game_link_box">
            <form action="/game/{{id}}" id="{{id}}" class="enter-form">
                <div class="game_name">{{name}}</div>
                <input type="password" required class="password_input" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호"/>
                <input type="submit" value="참여!"/>
            </form>
        </li>
        {{/games}}
    </ul>
</section>
<section class="buttons__container">
    <a href="/">뒤로가기!</a>
</section>
<script src="/scripts/search-game.js"></script>
<script src="/scripts/enter-game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
